  "text": "The FDA also cooperates with Veteran's Affairs, the Department of Defense, and the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services on the Federal Partner Collaboration (FPC), which provides access to federally owned healthcare data [CITATION_1] . This collaboration allows the FDA to assess the safety and effectiveness of products in unique and potentially vulnerable populations.",
